@startuml
skinparam shadowing false

title Plugin Lifecycle

actor User
participant Daqster
participant QPluginManager
participant Plugin as P

User -> Daqster : Start Application
Daqster -> QPluginManager : loadAll()
QPluginManager -> P : instantiate
P --> QPluginManager : initialize()
QPluginManager --> Daqster : plugin ready
Daqster --> User : UI available

== Shutdown ==
Daqster -> QPluginManager : unloadAll()
QPluginManager -> P : shutdown()
P --> QPluginManager : cleanup done
QPluginManager --> Daqster : all unloaded

@enduml